^ "Worlds USPTO PTAB verdict 2 Claims allowed 7493558". Scribd. Archived from the original on December 1, 2016. Retrieved 2016-11-30. 
^ "Update: Bungie Agrees to 10-Year Deal with Activision". Game Rant. 2010-04-29. Archived from the original on December 1, 2016. Retrieved 2016-11-30. 


